            <lg xml:id="TK1052">
<l>iṉpa moruvark kiratta lirantavai </l>
<l>tuṉpa muṟāa variṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even begging may be pleasant, if what is begged for is obtained without grief (to him that begs).</l>
            </lg>
